Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.23,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Shima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.58,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Saki-san. Yuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.90,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,If you're waiting for Misae, she'll be absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.58,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,She called Saki this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.78,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,She said she caught a cold and so she'll be absent from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.35,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.68,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,So something did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.90,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,It's unreal that Misae would skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.98,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Could it be that Igarashi-kun told her... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.25,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,I see. So she got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:38.45,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Poor Misae.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.24,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,But hey, Shima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:47.22,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,I think a boy like you is a better match for Misae than Igarashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.61,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Comfort Misae for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.31,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,I'll call her out to the park later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.83,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.83,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Forever With You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.41,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Sagara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.14,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sh-Shima-kun. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:57.62,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Um, Sagara-sa... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.28,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.94,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:05.27,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Love is like a firework from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:06.66,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:11.07,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's more beautiful for it to go to pieces and scatter far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.56,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.96,Default-alt,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.28,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.59,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.34,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Then in case you don't find paper in the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.81,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Are you being considerate or inconsiderate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.52,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're speaking complete nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.65,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I bet Yuki and Saki told you to say all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:36.29,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.32,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You would never say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.41,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why don't you say something original?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.54,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.04,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.42,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:59.67,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Probably... because I feel I'm responsible for the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:03.68,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You have nothing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:08.43,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Thinking back, I think there's a ton of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.31,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.93,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But really, the reason I'm depressed is because of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.04,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.82,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.65,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Are you thinking this is your chance to have me fall for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Like I said it would be, yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.16,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:42.89,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Of course. You only came to return a favor;\Nit's not like you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.43,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.10,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,So, you do like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:56.66,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.55,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.08,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,So hey. What do you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:16.21,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Things like you yelling at me and worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:21.59,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Also, whenever you put me in a wrestling hold,\NI can smell your good scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.89,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,...and I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.22,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't think that last one was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:26.94,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.58,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Forget about apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:31.80,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.81,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.06,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.83,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Um... You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.79,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Misae!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.12,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Do you have time today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:53.76,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,There's a new ice cream shop\Non the other side of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:56.13,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sorry. Today's... See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:01.47,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,He's waiting and all, so I'd feel bad if I didn't go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.03,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.06,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,I guess things are going well for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.01,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.26,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:15.91,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yup. Believe it or not, I'm the school's first female Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.02,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Wow, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.42,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,The Autumn Festival is coming up soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:26.53,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Our school's helping out with it, too, so things are a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.12,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Autumn Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.85,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.73,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,...if you don't have any plans on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.26,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,...would you want to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.62,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,To the Autumn Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.13,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'll be discovered... I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.58,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.86,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I see. So Misae-san's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.53,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Yes. She's attending a Student Council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.43,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,She wanted us to tell you that she'll be out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.56,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I want to see her working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.86,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Actually, he looks so cute it's starting to make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:17.44,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll deliver this love quietly to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.44,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,That's Yoshino-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.16,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,He's as popular as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.46,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey you. Which class are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.71,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you around. Are you a transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.57,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Want me to give you a tour of the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:34.10,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,That's fine. We're taking her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.76,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No need to be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to flirt with her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.86,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,We're really fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.86,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Then at least tell me her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.12,Default-alt,Girls,0,0,0,,Go on, Shima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.98,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,No, it's really all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, wait you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.73,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.77,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Moving on to the next topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.13,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Regarding the student who brings in guitars and has live concerts in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:03.57,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,There's no problem with singing, but it shouldn't be done in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.57,Default-alt,Shi,0,0,0,,She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.79,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Do you need something in the Student Council room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.17,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,If you need something inside, go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.29,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,It's not as though it is off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:15.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.13,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Sagara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.30,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Ibuki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.61,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you in the middle of your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.70,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,It seems she has something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.27,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Wow, she's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I didn't know we had a girl like this at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.11,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.85,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You have something you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.06,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Say what's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.67,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's the Student Council's job to listen to the students' opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.25,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.74,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:54.92,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I want you to be with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:01.18,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Um... What relationship do the two of you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.35,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,That was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.61,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.28,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Maybe she figured out that it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.46,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.97,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Misae might like you more in that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.04,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,How could that be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:31.42,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.46,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.62,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Hey, Shima-kun. Are you busy after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:46.22,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,We were just saying that we should go visit your place after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:53.39,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Oh, so Misae hasn't been to your place yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.00,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,This sense of superiority from visiting the home before the girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.56,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Let's brag to Misae later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.49,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.36,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,You don't feel like it after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.52,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.96,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.48,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,...where my home is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.97,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Hey, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.18,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Don't scare us with a joke like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.20,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.69,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Say, "I'm home."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.72,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you Katsuki's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.58,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:47.07,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.83,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Please come in and offer incense for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.35,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.22,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.86,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,The real Shima Katsuki is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:10.35,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm not actually Shima Katsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.03,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:13.52,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.08,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.35,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,There's a story behind this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.00,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Is there anything we can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.43,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Then at least remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.77,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,We believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.96,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Because to us, you are Shima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.35,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we are your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:52.38,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.99,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,We'll keep this from Misae.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:12:00.25,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,If there's something you have to tell her,\Nmake sure you let her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:00.78,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.72,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I finally remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm not Shima Katsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.77,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That was the name of the person dearest to me. {ep 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:29.89,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,We spent much time together,\Nand he left me with his last wish. {ep 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:35.59,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I came to grant that wish. {ep 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.53,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.91,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:51.36,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's fine, since I'm always the one making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.93,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,The girl from yesterday was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.70,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.24,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Of course. We see each other every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.45,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Was I a bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's fine. I bet it was Yuki and Saki who made you do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.00,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:19.07,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Yes. Since that's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.74,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,See? There's a light that grants a wish in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.38,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,What? It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.84,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Maybe there was nothing there to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:34.49,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If not, it means that it's not necessary for me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:40.24,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What's important is for us to be happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.43,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,But this is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.13,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.05,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.52,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You have a wish in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.48,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.77,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,So here's the wish you so wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.39,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,...love me forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:11.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Please continue to love me forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.15,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,That's what I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.75,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sorry. Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.94,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Looks like I really did love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:45.59,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Though it was only for a short period of time, the time we spent together was precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.22,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I liked Yuki-san and Saki-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.19,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I loved the time we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.54,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be a copy of what you said to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.14,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Gosh, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.35,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.12,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're really one of those people who can't be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.38,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.91,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.39,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:24.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I-I'll go buy something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.40,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.76,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.10,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shima-ku-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.32,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.27,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.76,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.03,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Farewell, Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:22.62,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I will continue to love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.54,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yep, I'm back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.66,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah, the boy's dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,No plans for anything like that at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.43,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's not that I can't forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:56.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I guess that's how my life works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:02.08,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's all meet up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,With Yuki, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.52,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.37,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You decided to make this your home, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.42,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You like being with me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't particularly like cats, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:29.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,That was stupid. Why am I thinking of a fairytale-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.87,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're a really strange cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.00,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You had a good nap there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.95,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You looked like my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:51.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's getting late, so let's make our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:58.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sorry we stayed for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:03.02,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Make sure you have him take you to the Autumn Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you show me that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you do have a name after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So there are things you want me to tell her, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:32.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You've had something on your mind since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:36.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been thinking about how to let\NMisae-san know about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's Misae-san's kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is there something you still want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.04,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,And her boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Misae-san. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.23,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.48,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Man, I'm out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Could you fix the way you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Did you come to the festival with your cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:12.99,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,No. He suddenly dashed out and I came chasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.25,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I have no idea what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.20,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Gosh. I really have to keep my eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.42,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hey, come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:34.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think he's wanted to come to this festival with you for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.46,Default-alt,Mis,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:40.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Last night, I think I heard his voice in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:47.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He said, "I'm sorry I couldn't be with you until the end of the festival."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:50.83,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.62,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Did he say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:59.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And, "As you wished, I'll always be with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.59,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying I would go on a date with a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:14.44,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But I guess I'll play with you a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's one more thing to tell you, Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:24.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He wishes for you to find your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:29.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After all, he's like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:38.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. He is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.21,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,He was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.36,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try and enjoy another youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:56.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll tell you about the dream I had last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A wondrous love story from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.02,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.42,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:22.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,My current master is not the same as you,\Nbut she's a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.46,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,But she makes me worry at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.00,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Was I able to meet the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:38.67,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Was I able to fulfill the promise we made?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:44.56,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Now, it's been too long, and I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:49.68,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,But right now, I want to remain like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.01,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Please allow me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:22:05.61,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Please allow me to be with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.68,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(981.818,452.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:45.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:47.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:50.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.27,0:23:52.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He just wants to act bossy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:56.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He'll be as snotty as possible to anyone who's weaker than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:09.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,384.75)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:09.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,767.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Where She Belongs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come with us.
